{"ts":"2026-07-06T08:03:03.701Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/437\n\n## Problem\nEvery CLI mutation echoes the full updated item + full `changed_fields` by default (368 B for a trivial create vs 29 B `--id-only` — 12.7x). MCP is already compact by default (`changed_field_count`, `idOnly`/`fullChangedFields` opt-ins), so the CLI is the more verbose surface and inconsistent with MCP.\n\n## Proposed fix\nMake CLI mutation default lean: `{ id, status, changed_field_count }` (+ `close_reason` on close). Full echo behind `--full` / `--full-changed-fields`; existing `--id-only`/`--quiet` stay. Config knob (e.g. `output_lean_mutations`) so the default is project-tunable; respect back-compat for scripts via config.\n\n## Definition of done\nLean default (or config-flipped default) with parity spec vs MCP compact output; docs/AGENTS.md updated; contracts:update run; measured token reduction recorded on this item."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-nilh"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-437: make lean mutation output the CLI default (parity with MCP compact envelope)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood GH-437: CLI mutations echo the full item (12.7x vs --id-only) while MCP is compact by default; align CLI default with MCP. Duplicate check: compact mutation output PR (2026-05-26) shipped suppressor flags only; no open item flips the default."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:cli","gh-issue","token-efficiency"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:03.701Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:03.701Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":120},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"CLI mutations default (or config-default) to id/status/changed_field_count; --full opt-ins restore old echo; MCP-parity spec green; measured reduction recorded"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"982cbaf41adc2ca4d49caab649339b5cd723a88520331c56fa94e14257bbf748","message":""}
